                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.512/460: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-12-09T12:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 9, 1926—noon</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received December 9—7:54 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>606. My 598 of December 4th, 4 p.m.</p>
                <list>
                    <label>1.</label>
                    <item>I am informed by the British Chargé that the British Government has
                        authorized action toward immediate implementing of Washington Treaty and
                        instructed him that it considers that action as suggested in my 598 is an
                        obvious and necessary next step.</item>
                    <label>2.</label>
                    <item>He further gave me to understand that his Government while gladly
                        approving this way out of the dilemma is resolved nevertheless in case that
                        that course of action should prove unsuccessful, to compound with the
                        Cantonese in the matter of the illegal surtaxes.</item>
                </list>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">MacMurray</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
